\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊度揾"},{"pid":"17d44c3b5e5ca11c4b7acd867cce336ec4d374fa","tid":450570,"uid":3914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"王祖藍夠溝到李亞男啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6998dafdf46954b4d9b199b2439fdb59d76f9a","tid":450570,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢真人係咪都係咁傻 高學歷傻佬</blockquote><br />\n係,次次同佢食飯佢叫晒D野食,上咗菜先話唔要,搞到我幾老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908d2c25e921fb8d410a292ceebf779dfb203270","tid":450570,"uid":78900,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國女演員，Hallstatt Nordid類型（北歐人種Hallstatt類型）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mrbean.wikia.com/wiki/Irma_Gobb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrbean.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2FIrma_Gobb&d=KCsqmQiBR0D6uDrfmw%2FqxgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=8228f1e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://mrbean.wikia.com/wiki/Irma_Gobb</a></blockquote><br />\n又係你條毒撚龍友<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/203341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F203341_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=742a9bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecc9be60810d214b36a6a39608832c399ea03894","tid":450570,"uid":22898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢真人係咪都係咁傻 高學歷傻佬</blockquote><br />\n係,次次同佢食飯佢叫晒D野食,上咗菜先話唔要,搞到我幾老尷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有冇將啲野食收埋曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204eeac7d7854c082b0a7aa9c80b4407699862d2","tid":450570,"uid":1159,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:39:43.000Z","msg":"愛瑪（Irma Gobb）\t<br />\nMatilda Ziegler飾演。戇豆先生的女朋友，亦是他的青梅竹馬，是個漂亮金髮眼鏡女郎，她和戇豆先生一樣，也有一隻泰迪熊娃娃綠蒂（Lottie），有時候也會帶小丑回魂出去玩，有時候也會和戇豆一樣為泰迪舉辦生日派對。"},{"pid":"3c1e4cdc098745d8a588482d1dca83d582759341","tid":450570,"uid":1007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"由細細個第一次睇到而家都諗咗好多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你計卡通版 佢有集有講過 青梅竹馬嚟 係條女自己追Mr. Bean 但點解鍾意就唔記得咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667e18cb2387cacdae54b81fb85f1d65a3274b7c","tid":450570,"uid":28871,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:51:29.000Z","msg":"拍劇"},{"pid":"f7de82bbd180ef0d7e7eb2a7a3d355687f721ee0","tid":450570,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愛瑪（Irma Gobb）\t<br />\nMatilda Ziegler飾演。戇豆先生的女朋友，亦是他的青梅竹馬，是個漂亮金髮眼鏡女郎，她和戇豆先生一樣，也有一隻泰迪熊娃娃綠蒂（Lottie），有時候也會帶小丑回魂出去玩，有時候也會和戇豆一樣為泰迪舉辦生日派對。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n青梅竹馬都等於易溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf20f6c3dbf16ef7bca763337904b7b988d3b93b","tid":450570,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幽默</blockquote><br />\n咁我點解溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個樣？"},{"pid":"e798223229eb46e7e21ecee1a0d69c8ff6e0ae37","tid":450570,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"tum到條女笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978221dadfc201b114e33605d157ed379724b96e","tid":450570,"uid":100347,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>才華</blockquote><br />\n我夠有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\