/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我知可能有人誤會左我講佢現實生活。所以已經出埋圖，強調返啲Mr bean既情節，估唔到大家都係咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放鬆啲啦連登仔，唔好吓吓踩底人拎成功感"},{"pid":"9cd2994e816d5439ad453895511ca9c0db845660","tid":450570,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幽默</blockquote><br />\n咁我點解溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個樣就幽默"},{"pid":"83ea46ee74da1d05e0ffa92f3085d8f13b9161e2","tid":450570,"uid":22898,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:17:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/28/214056_1dd9cab70afc5d8d94fc27461cece011.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F28%2F214056_1dd9cab70afc5d8d94fc27461cece011.jpg&h=5edd0532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n明？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得啦得啦"},{"pid":"89a96342d90e63207a80bb05093a8ff4779803cd","tid":450570,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幽默</blockquote><br />\n咁我點解溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個樣就幽默"},{"pid":"f670fd4f002b75fbe4baec1d9b19eabf1d2c3533","tid":450570,"uid":22898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幽默</blockquote><br />\n咁我點解溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個樣就幽默</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇第二句<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51730d81134733a6fdc31d1f04c5e5c3e36b7f8c","tid":450570,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幽默</blockquote><br />\n咁我點解溝唔到女<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" cla